Package: ttmouse
Title: Project Mouse RNA-seq Data onto a Pre-built TimeTeller Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Vadim", "Vasilyev", email = "vadim.vasilyev@warwick.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Engine for a public tool that projects raw mouse RNA-seq count
    matrices onto pre-built TimeTeller circadian-clock models and returns the
    model results (predicted phase and dysfunction). Provides file ingestion,
    the frozen TPM preprocessing contract, model loading and gene validation,
    and the projection wrapper. The Shiny front-end and Docker packaging are
    added in later phases.
